seo_en: yccms, rce vulnerability, remote code execution, vulnerability detection
summary: 该插件用于检测yccms系统是否存在远程代码执行（RCE）漏洞，通过构造特定的请求来验证漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the yccms system has a Remote Code Execution (RCE) vulnerability by constructing specific requests to verify the existence of the vulnerability.
